title: GoodSync 7.61 + KeyGen
description:
GoodSync Pro v7.1.9      
             (c) Siber Systems Inc. 
    
 Software  that automatically syncs between desktops,   
 laptops, and external drives.                           
                                                           
 * Never Lose Your Emails, Photos, MP3s, etc...           
                                                                
 GoodSync  combines  bulletproof  reliability with an      
 extremely    easy   to  use  interface  to  compare,    
 photos, iTunes, MP3s, and other important files.       
                                                          
 * Automatically Sync or Back Up to Multiple Devices       
 Automatically synchronize and back up your important      
 files    between  desktops,  laptops,  servers,  and     
 external  drives  over  a  network  or the Internet.  
 Using  an  innovative  synchronization  algorithm --  
 GoodSync is years ahead of the pack when it comes to   
 synchronization.                                        
 
* Easy and Automated                                      
  
 Keep your files up to date with one click, eliminate      
 information  clutter,  and  most  importantly  begin    
 enjoying  your  peace  of  mind,  knowing  that your   
 financial  documents,  work files, emails, contacts,      
 photos,   iTunes,   MP3s,   and   other   data   are      
 synchronized and backed up.
